# FireGuard â€“ Fire Detection Robot

## Description
**FireGuard** is an autonomous robot that detects fire or smoke in homes or offices. It alerts users immediately, helping prevent fire damage and protect lives.

## Technologies Used
- Arduino UNO  
- Smoke & Temperature Sensors  
- Raspberry Pi  
- Python  

## Key Features
- Early fire detection  
- Real-time notifications  
- Portable and easy-to-deploy  

## My Role
Built the hardware, implemented sensor detection logic, and tested alert system.

